replies.body:
Totally agree, nerf this guy ->{{champion:238}} 

Who else has the power to dive (teleport onto) you under tower, crap on your face and teleport back without taking any risk of even being shot by the tower? Answer: No one.

He has no counter play about him, it's a tele in, melt, tele out. Not to mention, like Azir he is a high early dmg lane bully with ridiculously ranged poke that doesn't make him even move out of safety and never falls off late. I about gagged when Rito said he was a "healthy assassin" in their last patch notes.
